name: Necroharmonic caseless CD release (CDs without Jewel Cases )
description:
CD releases Without Jewel Cases


These cart items are made for WORLD orders who would like to purchase CDs  , without the use of a JEWEL CASE / CD box

since Postage rates with the use of CD Jewel cases raise the rates to our Worldwide customers , we would like to offer here some titles of Necroharmonic  WITHOUT the CD Jewel cases , so that that postage rates can be lower for these World orders. 

The band options are on the drop down menu. 

MORE BANDS CDs TO FOLLOW !! 

Cds will be shipped without cases / with bookets and tray in a very light cardboard backing , so not to raise the postage rates. 

Multiple Cds can be bought at a much lower rate then ever before...


**** please note at check out ,

1. you can use the " add to cart " red button to check the postage on 1st Cd , and then mutiple ones. 

2. The photo ( in the cart check out page )  will show the GUT cd cover

3 ) The CD you would like to purchase caseless will show up below in name as the option  ( please double check your option! thanks ! )

name: Goreaphobia " Vile Beast of Abomination " CD
description:
GOREAPHOBIA " VILE BEAST OF ABOMINATION " CD   

Philadelphia's Goreaphobia reunited with its original 1990  era Line up in the year 2004 ,  to record 2 classic tracks that never got recorded back in 1990 , as well as 2 new ones !! This also contains the  " Omen of Masochism " 7 ep , and " Morbidious Pathology " session , as well as 3 Live Tracks from 1990 !!!  This is a must have release ! This has a HUGE booklet  with a History of the band ,  Flyers , Photos , Lyrics , etc....and art by Drew Elliott

name: Interment " Forward To The Unknown " T shirt
description:
Interment " Forward To The Unknown " T shirt





Sold out..discontinued 

T shirt edition , limited to 50 ( pressed 32 ) 


no repress of this limited Swedish death metal Tee


This artwork originally graced the early demo tape of Interment entitled " Forward to the Unknown " . an all time classic Swedish death recording and a great artwork as well. 


Later in 2010 , was  released officially as a CD discography entitled  : INTERMENT " Where Death Will Increase " CD , was a discography CD from 1991 - 1994 and contained the demo tapes and a CD booklet about Interment early times  , including the -  Forward to the Unknown - demo recording.

name: Disma " The Manifestation " Sweatshirt
description:
Disma " The Manifestation "  Sweatshirt

Pullover Fleece Longlseeve  with cover of EP ' The Manifestation '

sold = 4 garments , item to be deleted from stock at 12 garments , Limited edition pressing on Sweatshirt 


Necroharmonic released the 7 " ep Vinyl of Disma which in fact contains members who played in Funebrarum , Incantation and more...  founded by Bill Venner , who shared the same hometown as the founder of NH records ....  Bill drew the logo of the label Necroharmonic as well as other cult logos of Incantation , Abhorrence ( fin )  and one logo for GUT... Disma singer Craig Pillard also sang on the now classic Incantation album ' Onward to Golgotha " as well as forming bands like Womb , Disciples of Mockery , Methadrone , and even playing in Evoken !
